trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPointCollection"></xref> class.
The default constructor initializes the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPointCollection> to an empty list.
trans-unit.target: 默认构造函数初始化<xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPointCollection>为空列表。</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPointCollection>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPointCollection"></xref> class by using a list of user track points.
trans-unit.target: 初始化的新实例<xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPointCollection"></xref>类使用的用户跟踪点的列表。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPointCollection> is initialized to contain the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint> objects specified in `points`.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPointCollection>初始化后将包含<xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint>中指定的对象`points`。</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPointCollection>

trans-unit.source: points is a null reference ( in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: points为空引用 ( 在 Visual Basic 中)。
